SyntheticaJYTabbedPaneUI
public class BasicJYTabbedPaneUI
extends JYTabbedPaneUI
implements java.awt.event.FocusListener

Basic UI implementation for JYTabbedPane. By default the style of JTabbedPane is used, however it's possible to customize the style without modifying JTabbedPane style by named default properties and by specifying a separate painter. To simplify maintainability a panel hierarchy is used to manage all needed areas and subcomponents. Optional UI-properties:

  • JYTabbedPane.closeButtonStrategy - String, default is "NONE"
  • JYTabbedPane.showScrollButtons - Boolean, default is True
  • JYTabbedPane.showPopupButton - Boolean, default is True
  • JYTabbedPane.tabGap - Integer, default is 0
  • JYTabbedPane.horizontalTabAlignment - Integer, default is 2 (SwingConstants.LEFT)
  • JYTabbedPane.verticalTabAlignment - Integer, default is 1 (SwingConstants.TOP)
  • JYTabbedPane.tabStyle - String, default is "COMMON"
  • JYTabbedPane.tabControlsPosition - String, default is "TRAILING"
  • JYTabbedPane.tabControlsShowStrategy - String, default is "AS_NEEDED"
  • JYTabbedPane.tabScrollAnimationEnabled - Boolean, default is True
  • JYTabbedPane.tabReorderByDraggingEnabled - Boolean, enabled/disable tab reorder by dragging, default is True
  • JYTabbedPane.tab.selectedBold - Boolean, paint selected tab text bold, default is False
  • JYTabbedPane.tab.closeButtonGap - Integer, gap between text and close button, default is 6
  • JYTabbedPane.tab.autoScrollDelay - Integer, auto scroll delay while dragging tab, default is 250
  • JYTabbedPane.tab.minimumSize - Integer, minimum tab width, default is -1 which means value isn't set
  • JYTabbedPane.tab.maximumSize - Integer, maximum tab width, default is -1 which means value isn't set
  • JYTabbedPane.overlapTabsInvers - Boolean, overlap tabs at the right side, default is False
  • JYTabbedPane.tabsStretchedEnabled - Boolean, stretch tap size across complete tabbPane width, default is False
  • JYTabbedPane.tabRotationEnabled - Boolean, rotate left/right placed tabs, default is True
  • JYTabbedPane.tabsPanel.croppedEdge.size - Integer, size of cropped edge, default is 3, 0 means disabled
  • JYTabbedPane.tabsPanel.croppedEdge.background - Color, Background color of croppedEdge, default is panel background
  • JYTabbedPane.tabsPanel.croppedEdge.foreground - Color, Line color of croppedEdge, default is Color(0x40000000, true)
  • JYTabbedPane.tabsPanel.avoidCroppedTabs - Boolean, default is False
  • JYTabbedPane.dragArrowIcon [.left | .right | .up | .down] - String, Icon path or className
  • JYTabbedPane.buttonFactory.className - String, defines used button factory, see ButtonFactory for additional UI-properties
  • JYTabbedPane.popupMenu.forceIconSpace - Boolean, reserve space for icon in the popupMenu even if no icon is set, default is False

    • Version:
    1.44, 05.04.2011
